Ryan Says ‘Real Money’ in Insurance Is With Specialty Coverage

-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 
2011-09-27T13:51:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/ryan-says-real-money-in-insurance-is-with-specialty-coverage.html
Patrick Ryan, the chief executive
officer of Ryan Specialty Group, said investors prefer insurance
firms that can distinguish themselves through unique offerings.  “They want the approach of differentiating the abilities
of the underwriters and brokers,” Ryan, the former CEO of  Aon
Corp. (AON) , said today at the 3rd Annual Reactions Magazine North
America Conference in  New York . “The real money in our industry
is in the specialties.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  